<p>[4] <a href="http://www.worldproutassembly.org/archives/2008/07/appendix_ii_fro.html" target="_blank">APPENDIX II from &#8216;KILLING HOPE&#8217; by William Blum</a> (<a href="http://www.worldproutassembly.org/archives/2008/07/appendix_ii_fro.html" target="_blank">http://www.worldproutassembly.org/archives/2008/07/appendix_ii_fro.html</a>).   </p>
