racityvoice.com/?tag=spain" rel="tag">Spain</a>, <a href="http://veracityvoice.com/?tag=thanksgiving" rel="tag">Thanksgiving</a>, <a href="http://veracityvoice.com/?tag=turkey" rel="tag">Turkey</a>, <a href="http://veracityvoice.com/?tag=war" rel="tag">War</a>, <a href="http://veracityvoice.com/?tag=wmd" rel="tag">WMD</a></span></p>
